WEBVTT

00:03.013 --> 00:05.848
The last words I said to my
daughter were angry.

00:05.873 --> 00:07.672
Some of the practices that
were taking place

00:07.673 --> 00:09.700
during my son's tenure were unacceptable.

00:09.725 --> 00:11.172
Maggie? It's Kathryn.

00:11.173 --> 00:13.848
Max's son wants to dish the dirt.

00:13.873 --> 00:16.045
You're going to accuse him of what?

00:16.085 --> 00:18.484
Blackmail, theft, illegal surveillance.

00:18.485 --> 00:20.123
On what evidence?

00:20.124 --> 00:21.836
Caden's confession.

00:21.837 --> 00:25.436
I will spread your most damaging
secrets all over the news.

00:25.480 --> 00:28.382
I've heard Orla talking about
investigations and tribunals

00:28.382 --> 00:29.861
ever since she arrived here.

00:29.862 --> 00:31.061
It's not real.

00:31.062 --> 00:33.101
How did you know
we were having this meeting?

00:33.102 --> 00:35.101
You have all the evidence right there.

00:35.102 --> 00:37.782
Hand it over and Caden will go to jail.

00:38.626 --> 00:40.021
I clicked on a link,

00:40.022 --> 00:43.621
and it was about
the downfall of democracy.

00:43.622 --> 00:46.370
I know Britain, I know my home,
I know my people.

00:46.371 --> 00:48.446
All I see are lines.

00:48.447 --> 00:50.655
Are you inside or outside?

00:50.680 --> 00:53.782
If you agree with her,
she's your best friend.

00:53.783 --> 00:55.720
If you disagree...

